import pandas as pd
from pycaret.classification import *
from pycaret.classification import setup, compare_models, pull, predict_model, tune_model
df = pd.read_csv('VExtr_FDRClust.csv')
data = df
target_col = 'Class'
#print(df)

def supports_feature_importance(model):
    return hasattr(model, 'coef_') or hasattr(model, 'feature_importances_')
